sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant AD as Administrator
  participant NV as New Server
  participant BS as bootstrap_monitored_vm.sh
  participant CS as Central Stack
  participant ES as Elasticsearch
  participant AA as ARIA (assets)
  AD->>NV: run bootstrap script (prompts: identity, central IP)
  BS->>NV: install Wazuh agent, Suricata, Falco, Filebeat, Telegraf
  BS->>NV: write forwarding config (host identity fields)
  BS->>CS: register Wazuh agent (1514/1515)
  NV->>ES: forward logs/alerts/metrics (HTTPS 9200 via central)
  BS-->>AD: print ARIA asset payload (source_config_json)
  AD->>AA: create MonitoredAsset (asset_id, index patterns)
  AA->>ES: validate per-source telemetry present
  ES-->>AA: index/document counts
  AA-->>AD: validation_status = ok | partial | missing
